{
  "stem": "2067.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And they haven't seen me in a week or so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "I wanted to protect my parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And slowly but surely a plan ripened in Max and my mind to try to escape from Holland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "The shortest escape route was through Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And we had heard rumors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And a second cousin of mine who lived in Holland, he had informed me of that possibility to go-- to get to Antwerp in Belgium, and that there there where so-called [NON-ENGLISH]-- a French word for a smuggler-- who could take people to non-occupied France.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "You may know that after France was defeated, Hitler created an occupied zone which was the western part of France.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And the eastern part of France was the non-occupied or Vichy France zone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "That was on the French government.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "Of course, the Germans still had their-- their influence there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "But it was still-- had still a certain extent of freedom for escapees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When I told [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "Dottie ?] of my plan, she said, don't do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "You think that only young men are in danger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "I have the feeling that it will be every single one-- men, women, children, anyone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "Well, I tried to convince her that all measures that had been taken so far were mainly against young men.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "Our parents, who hadn't like everyone else, hadn't recognized yet the deadly danger that all of us were in, they urged us-- me, of course, and Max-- his parents-- to leave.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "Before I left in November '41 I decided to go to [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "Dottie's ?] father and ask for her hand, the old-fashioned way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "And I knew there would be-- there would be no problem, because I noticed that they liked me very much.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
